    "text": [
        "Dear Mr Daniel Defoe,",
        "I am writing this letter to ask your favour. I am John Abraham. I completed a presentation skill course at your college last year and my student ID number is 213423. My instructor was Mr David Brown and Barbara Catharine. During the course, I had made several reports and done assignments that I need very urgently.",
        "In the next month, I am going to join a new organization. Seeing my curriculum vita that I have completed the presentation skills course, my new employer asked me to submit copies of my reports and assignments. But unfortunately, I do not find them. Maybe the copies were somehow missed when I moved to this new city for the job.",
        "Therefore, it would be very appreciated if you send me copies of reports and assignments that I had done during the course as early as possible. And I would like to bear the postal charges. I look forward to hearing you soon.",
        "Yours sincerely,",
        "John Abraham"
